import Head from 'next/head'
import Navbar from './Navbar'

const Layout = (props) => ( <
    div >
    <
    Head >
    <
    title > My App < /title> <
    link rel = "stylesheet"
    href = "/static/bootstrap.min.css" / >
    <
    /Head> <
    div className = "container" > < Navbar / > < /div> <
    div className = "container" > { props.children } < /div> <
    /div>
);

export default Layout;
